OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSouth Africans face jail if
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fchildren not in school     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, South Africa's parliament has passed a 
OL,6, major education bill that could see    
OL,7, parents face prison if their children  
OL,8, are not in school.                     
OL,10,FUnder the Basic Education Laws         
OL,11,FAmendment (Bela), they could be jailed 
OL,12,Ffor up to 12 months if their children  
OL,13,Fare truant, or if they are not enrolled
OL,14,Fwhen they reach school age.            
OL,16,FBela also introduces a ban on corporal 
OL,17,Fpunishment in all schools.             
OL,19,FIt is the biggest education overhaul   
OL,20,Fsince the end of apartheid in 1994.    
